Key Match Events: Aaron Judge hit his 55th home run of the season
Gleyber Torres hit a solo homer
Luis Gil allowed four runs on five hits while walking three and striking out five over 5.1 innings
Ian Hamilton gave up a two-run double in the sixth
Post-Match Reflections: Aaron Judge continues building on his American League MVP candidacy
Clay Holmes secured the win by retiring the side in order to close out the game
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jasson Dominguez hit his second home run of the season
Giancarlo Stanton drove in runs in back-to-back games
The Yankees completed the sweep of the Athletics
